init
    set systick to once a millisecond // done

loop
    if (normal)
        flash green
        flash blue
    else
        flash green and blue

When button pressed
    Reset counter

When button released
    save old counter
    clear counter
    set normal = false

When clock tick // done
    Counter++
    if (!normal && counter > old counter)
        normal = true

Button Press Subroutine
